      "span_text": "They have found that education did improve physician compliance in the use of lung protective ventilatory strategies, with a tidal volume decline within 6 months after intervention from 9.8 ml/kg ± 2.0 at baseline to 8.1 ±1.7 ml/ kg. The feedback and education program focused on lungprotective MV, with an emphasis on adjusting tidal volumes to predicted body weight (PBW)."
